text: Hickey Ranch is a location near Lonetree in the Bridger Valley, Uinta County, Wyoming, United States.http://www.fallingrain.com/world/US/WY/Hickey_Ranch.html The USGS locates its coordinates at N41.06301° W110.15265°. The ranch site was founded in 1908 by a French-Canadian settler named Eugene Hickey. ==References== Category:Geography of Wyoming
title: Hickey Ranch
